summary: 该插件用于检测SpringFramework JDK >= 9的CVE-2022-22965远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断目标是否存在漏洞并输出相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the CVE-2022-22965 Remote Code Execution vulnerability in SpringFramework with JDK >= 9. It sends specific requests to determine if the target is vulnerable and outputs related information.
